title: Hour 3 - LIV Tour Timing, Bill Plaschke
itunes:title: Hour 3 - LIV Tour Timing, Bill Plaschke
description:
Dan questions the timing of those who decided to join the LIV Tour after the U.S. Open finished. And he talks to Bill Plaschke about the latest reports about Freddie Freeman and how it is affecting the Los Angeles Dodgers.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
